Create OU's, User and Group

OU >

From Tools > Select Active Directory Users and Computer > Right click on domain name > New >
Organizational Unit > Give name > OK

User >

For User > Right click domain name > Select New > User > Give user name and login name > Next > 
Set Password(Check mark Password never expires) > Next > Finish

Group >

For Group > Right click domain name > select new > Group > Give Group Name > Ok

Add Member to Group >

For Add member to group > click group name > select members > Add > Give name on Enter the object 
names to select > Check name > OK
